item.title: Need help changing tele on death
item.dc:creator: @RaPz RaPz
item.description:
@RaPz wrote:

Go into your config.java and search for START_LOCATION_X then under it it should have the START_LOCATION_Y.
under that it says RESPAWN_X thats where you add where you want them to end up when they die.
public static final int RESPAWN_X = 3095; // when dead respawn here
public static final int RESPAWN_Y = 3472;
